name: Jette Feigenbaum
body:
## About me

* Born on January 28, 1991
* Can speak Estonian, English, French
* Interested in dogs, tumblr, photography, cooking, coding

## Freelance Projects

### Tenerife Real Estate

since December 2013

[Real estate website](http://tenerife24.ee) for property in Tenerife. Includes a back-end part where admin can add/change information, upload photos etc.

_Ruby on Rails, Postgres, Bootstrap, Sass, Google Maps_

## Personal Projects

### tunnekoera.ee

2011 - 2013

[Tunne Koera](http://tunnekoera.ee) Estonian Dog Magazine.

_Wordpress, HTML, CSS_

### jette.ee

2000 - present

I've had various versions of my [personal website](http://www.jette.ee) over time where I've had the chance to experiment with different front-end technologies and designs. 

_Middleman, Skrollr, HTML, CSS, jQuery, Git, Heroku, Bootstrap_

### Mobile apps

summer 2013

I have made three simple [mobile apps](https://play.google.com/store/apps/developer?id=Jette) for Android: Motivational Quotes, Decision Maker and Yes/No Generator.

_Javascript, HTML, CSS, Phonegap Build, Git, Bootstrap_

## Work experience
### Project manager in Desk Rock

Feb 2013 - Sept 2013

[Desk Rock](http://deskrock.ee) is an agile IT company which develops finance software with Ruby on Rails and Java. I did mostly project leading such as talking to clients and organizing developer team's work flow, but also support, coding and testing.

#### Contributions

##### Allkiri.ee

This is a digital signing portal. You can upload documents and share them for signing. I contributed with front-end development like cutting HTML. In the back-end I added translation functionality to the portal. Throughout the project I tested the features and gave design and usability ideas. Also started a new version of the portal with using Backbone.js for front-end. 

_HAML, CSS, Ruby on Rails, Javascript (jQuery, Backbone.js), Photoshop, PostgreSQL_

##### COFI 

COFI is an installment payments back-end system for managing applications, offers, contracts, payments and reports. I dealt with incoming feature requests, support and tested new features on the system by hand. Also created HTML versions of contracts for automatic creating of PDF's.

_HTML, Ruby on Rails, PostgreSQL_

##### Credit Card System

CCS is an application for managing Säästukaart+ credit card applications, contracts, cards, reports and account receivables. I did project leading for adding loan and installment payments to the CCS system - analyzing new incoming feature requests and also testing.

_Ruby on Rails, PostgreSQL_


### IT and marketing specialist in Koertekeskus

Jan 2012 - May 2012

As it was a small company, I really did everything from managing the company's website and Facebook profile to managing/writing newsletters with MailChimp and consulting the clients in buying products for their dogs.

## Been to

### Rails Girls 2013 Tallinn

Made a budget calculator app in Ruby on Rails.

_Ruby on Rails, Heroku, Git, Bootstrap_

## Education

### Biology in Tallinn University

from 2014

### IT systems development in The Estonian Information Technology College

2012-2013

_Introduction to programming with Java, Web applications etc._

### Ecology in Tartu University

2010-2011

_Behavior ecology, Zoo-semiotics, Organic chemistry, Genetics, Cell biology, Geology, Evolution, Intro to Zoology etc._

### Hugo Treffneri Gümnaasium (highschool)

2007-2010

_Emphasis on literature and history._
